data.description: Situated in a peaceful, well-established neighborhood, this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is move in ready. The home features a comfortable living room, galley kitchen, and dining area. The home is climate controlled through a fireplace insert, monitor heat, and mini splits in each bedroom. The master bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom for privacy and convenience, while the two additional bedrooms are ideal for family, guests, or a home office. With large front and back yards, this property is a retreat for families and individuals alike. The backyard is made complete with quality fencing, a covered patio, and mature trees. Alley access to the backyard makes yard work a breeze. Within walking distance to a neighborhood park and close proximity to schools and downtown, this home is both comfortable and functional. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this house your new home; schedule a viewing today!
